title: Ep. - 342 - JENNY MCCARTHY FROM MASKED SINGER KOVIE BIAKOLO REVIEWS THE BACHELOR
description:
Jenny McCarthy discusses this season of Masked Singer, the contestant she admittedly did not recognize, why her husband Donnie thinks he is a police officer, and the reason he has been buying sequin jackets.

 

Kovie Biakolo is a writer, journalist, editor, and multiculturalism scholar specializing in culture and identity. She reviews this season of The Bachelor.
